name: Mental health
tweet: Social anxiety isn’t just “hating talking to people”. It’s being scared of making phone calls, making appointments. Walking on the sidewalk because you feel like everyone is judging you. You have this unexplainable fear of going out in public. That you can’t explain or understand

name: Mental health
tweet: Anxiety Kills you. You can’t sleep. You can barely eat. You’re terrified to get out of bed in the morning. You can’t handle social situations. You’re scared to do anything because of the fear of making mistakes. No one knows how miserable you are on the inside, and it sucks.

name: Mental health
tweet: What people think causes Depression:  • Weakness  • Laziness   What ACTUALLY causes Depression:  • Trauma  • Bullying  • Low self esteem  • Abuse  Depression is a very complicated illness. You can’t just “snap out of it”. Depression is way more than being just sad and lazy.

name: Mental health
tweet: Having anxiety and depression is like being scared and tired at the same time. It’s the fear of failure, but no urge to be productive. It’s wanting friends, but hate socializing. It’s wanting to be alone, but not to wanting to be lonely. It’s feeling everything at once.

name: Mental health
tweet: What depression is REALLY like:   • No motivation  • No energy  • Laying bed for hours because you’re too tired to move  • Knowing you’re not alone but still feeling alone  • Considering suicide whenever any problem arises  • Crying all the time  • No sleep/too much sleep
